1.title: What Damien Wants, Damien Gets
1.plot: Damien sets out on a new venture to teach his interns the policies about new client. Meanwhile, the pressures of family intrudes on Damien's Life while he is trying to accomplish some extra curricular activities with a new lover.

2.title: Meet Damien's Family
2.plot: Damien Johnson is forced to visit his extended family in this monthly dinner that they attend to keep the family intoned with one another. However when two ends of the family spectrum meet there ends up being a quite interesting mixture of conversations and desires.

3.title: All in a Days Work
3.plot: Damien meets a new love interests while deciding to trust him employees with a multi-million dollar account. Everything goes haywire when miss communication and a little fun crosses the tables.

4.title: Therapeutic Tendencies
4.plot: Damien visits his therapist and realizes some interesting facts about himself. As the session progresses real life pressures mixed with Therapist Sals critiques leaves Damien with some pondering choices in his life.

5.title: Friends Are Therapeutic
5.plot: Getting a workout has never been so inviting. Treava decides to workout when the boys decide to watch a little TV. Things change when Philip decides he wants to workout a little more than his arms.

7.title: Treava the Diva
7.plot: Damien and Philip decide to get a morning workout in before meeting with their buddy Philip. But the Gym God had some other activities in store for them.

-1.title: Mama's House
-1.plot: Damien is on a search to find out what make him tick. Just when he thought he would have the perfect evening alone with his date. His mother says otherwise while assisting to give him some personal help. This episode evaluates the relationship between Damien and his mother while revisiting some old moments of their unconventional relationship. "Mama's House"

imdb.plot outline: Damien Johnson does exactly what he wants to do when he wants to do it, he is not your average guy. Damien believes that what you put out in the world is exactly what you get back with that said. He does not allow anything get in his way. But, as Damien is getting older he realizes his old ways aren't always what they are cracked up to be. The relationships that Damien encounter over the year forces him to realize something new about himself each time. This unpredictable guy is on a Quest to find exactly who he is and what he wants out of his life. Meanwhile, his family is not so giving in the amount of slack they allow from him. With his dating life and family life Damien's addictions are now catching up with him. Join the cast of Damien's Quest a not so predictable show about finding out who you are but not settling for what others say you must be.
